<eesti>Sadamateenuste osutamine sadamapassita </eesti>
<inglise>Provision of port services without port certificate </inglise>
<eesti>Sadama valdajale, kes osutab sadamateenuseid sadamapassita v&otilde;i sadamapassis toodud tingimustest erinevalt, - m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv 5000 - 100 000 krooni. </eesti>
<inglise>A fine of 5000 to 100 000 kroons shall be imposed on a port authority who provides port services without a port certificate or differently from the conditions provided therein. </inglise>
<eesti>(12.12.2001 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2003 - RT I 2002, 1, 1) </eesti>
